Nigerian musician, Paul Okoye and wife have named their newborn twins – a boy and girl – Nathan and Nadia Okoye. Their native, Igbo names are Obinna and Adaobi Okoye.
The new father of twins took to his Instagram page to share his joy saying his household is complete, so no more kids again. The twins were delivered in Atlanta, United States of America. Nathan and Nadia already have an elder brother, Paul’s first son – 4 year old Andre Okoye.
